1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:55,560 --> 00:00:56,759
Another nightmare?

3
00:01:01,820 --> 00:01:05,740
=Episode 12=

4
00:01:17,879 --> 00:01:18,680
Mr. Liu.

5
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:25,680
Hurry.

6
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:28,359
Talk.

7
00:01:28,599 --> 00:01:29,439
Lady Cheng'en has been found.

8
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:31,480
Go.

9
00:01:44,079 --> 00:01:44,879
Liu Xin.

10
00:01:45,439 --> 00:01:47,040
Just as Master Wu said,

11
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:50,040
neither you nor Lady Cheng'en
will leave here alive today.

12
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,599
Let's see about that.

13
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:55,680
Mr. Liu, go. Now.

14
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:57,840
Stop them. Take them alive.

15
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:58,519
Yes!

16
00:02:08,439 --> 00:02:09,159
My Lady, run!

17
00:02:11,719 --> 00:02:12,520
Xiaotao!

18
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:13,759
Go!

19
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:14,800
Xiaotao!

20
00:02:16,319 --> 00:02:16,879
Xiaotao!

21
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:17,400
Go!

22
00:02:17,759 --> 00:02:18,159
Go!

23
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,360
Hurry!

24
00:02:23,639 --> 00:02:24,439
Mr. Liu, go!

25
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,599
Protect Lady Cheng'en!

26
00:02:25,599 --> 00:02:26,280
Don't mind me!

27
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,439
The rest of you, chase them!

28
00:02:37,900 --> 00:02:43,820
(Silk Thread)

29
00:02:48,759 --> 00:02:49,759
Wait, Feng Da.

30
00:02:50,039 --> 00:02:51,840
You didn't say there'd be
this many people.

31
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,199
My place is small.

32
00:02:53,199 --> 00:02:54,400
Where can they stay?

33
00:02:54,599 --> 00:02:56,280
Jiaojiao, do me a solid.

34
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,599
What's a solid worth?

35
00:03:00,039 --> 00:03:01,879
Thank you for your trouble, Ms. Huang.

36
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:05,080
I've got plenty of room.

37
00:03:05,639 --> 00:03:07,919
Stay as long as you want.

38
00:03:08,759 --> 00:03:09,639
Take them to the back.

39
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,039
That costs extra.

40
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,280
Sure. Here.

41
00:03:13,759 --> 00:03:16,039
Okay. Come, come.

42
00:03:16,159 --> 00:03:17,400
Right this way.

43
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:18,479
Ms. Huang!

44
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,199
Open up!

45
00:03:19,599 --> 00:03:20,759
Get in, quick!

46
00:03:21,439 --> 00:03:21,879
Go!

47
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,840
Open up, or I'll break it down!

48
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,280
(Silk Thread)
Coming, coming!

49
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:29,800
(Silk Thread)
Mr. Wang.

50
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:31,719
Why the banging at this hour?

51
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:33,280
Here to pay your silk bill?

52
00:03:33,759 --> 00:03:34,360
Official business.

53
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:35,639
Seen anyone suspicious?

54
00:03:35,639 --> 00:03:36,360
Sure have.

55
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,360
Where?

56
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,400
Right here.

57
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,120
Aren't you someone?

58
00:03:40,199 --> 00:03:40,599
You!

59
00:03:40,759 --> 00:03:41,479
Mr. Wang,

60
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:42,639
Mr. Wang,

61
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,439
we found signs of the Yehu Gang.

62
00:03:44,719 --> 00:03:45,199
Let's go.

63
00:03:45,639 --> 00:03:46,319
Hold on.

64
00:03:46,759 --> 00:03:48,360
Did I say you could leave?
Pay up!

65
00:03:48,759 --> 00:03:50,240
Woman, you're obsessed with money!

66
00:04:02,039 --> 00:04:02,840
Your Highness,

67
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:06,000
Lady Cheng'en was broken out
of death row last night.

68
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:07,840
Only the maid, Xiaotao, remains.

69
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,039
This is a serious matter.

70
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:11,159
I dared not decide alone,

71
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:13,280
so I came to ask your wishes.

72
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,240
Broken out?

73
00:04:14,879 --> 00:04:15,599
Yu Ming,

74
00:04:15,599 --> 00:04:16,439
answer me.

75
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:18,680
How does someone get broken
out of death row?

76
00:04:19,879 --> 00:04:21,480
Forgive me, Your Highness!

77
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:25,639
I reduced the guards so as
not to disturb

78
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,199
Lady Cheng'en's peace.

79
00:04:28,279 --> 00:04:31,240
Do you know who took her?

80
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:32,279
No.

81
00:04:33,439 --> 00:04:35,639
I only meant to teach her a lesson.

82
00:04:36,079 --> 00:04:37,079
Who knew she...

83
00:04:38,279 --> 00:04:39,079
Yu Ming.

84
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,959
I give you three days.

85
00:04:41,759 --> 00:04:42,399
No.

86
00:04:42,839 --> 00:04:43,680
Two days.

87
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:47,000
Find Lady Cheng'en within two days.

88
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:47,759
Yes.

89
00:04:47,759 --> 00:04:51,279
If you fail, you and your men

90
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:53,439
will lose your heads
when the Prince returns.

91
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:54,959
I understand.

92
00:04:55,279 --> 00:04:56,360
I'll take my leave.

93
00:04:56,839 --> 00:04:58,040
Then, what about her?

94
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:00,040
If Lady Cheng'en isn't found,

95
00:05:00,279 --> 00:05:02,279
treat her as an accomplice
to the jailbreak.

96
00:05:02,399 --> 00:05:02,959
Yes.

97
00:05:03,199 --> 00:05:03,959
Your Highness!

98
00:05:04,279 --> 00:05:05,040
Your Highness!

99
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,600
Your Highness,

100
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,079
Lady Cheng'en's murder charge

101
00:05:11,079 --> 00:05:12,040
and jailbreak

102
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:13,360
both seem suspicious.

103
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:14,720
You...

104
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:17,040
I dare not dwell on it.

105
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,079
But what matters most is

106
00:05:19,439 --> 00:05:22,160
that she must be here to receive
the Prince when he returns.

107
00:05:22,439 --> 00:05:23,600
Otherwise,

108
00:05:25,439 --> 00:05:28,560
he won't see how much
I've done for him

109
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:30,040
and how much I've endured.

110
00:05:31,439 --> 00:05:34,879
But ever since
she came to Jinxiu City,

111
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:36,879
many incidents have occurred in the city

112
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:39,800
and at Yanyu Embroidery House.

113
00:05:40,199 --> 00:05:42,279
I'll use her to keep
the Prince's favor first,

114
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,879
then decide on the rest.

115
00:05:46,079 --> 00:05:46,800
Master,

116
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,879
if there are future dangers,

117
00:05:50,079 --> 00:05:51,639
let me handle them.

118
00:05:52,639 --> 00:05:54,040
You poisoned yourself.

119
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:55,639
It terrified me.

120
00:05:55,759 --> 00:05:57,439
If it weren't convincing enough,

121
00:05:58,240 --> 00:06:00,279
how could I get her on death row?

122
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:03,639
But this time, thanks to
you following them,

123
00:06:03,959 --> 00:06:06,839
Wu Xin could take out Jia Yi.

124
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:09,879
You're so resourceful.

125
00:06:10,879 --> 00:06:14,279
But I wonder if Lady Cheng'en,
after being on death row,

126
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:17,199
will ever see the light of day again.

127
00:06:42,839 --> 00:06:45,480
You really care about your old friend.

128
00:06:47,439 --> 00:06:48,639
Of course not.

129
00:06:49,279 --> 00:06:52,360
I'm just worried for you.

130
00:06:54,439 --> 00:06:55,079
Master.

131
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:56,600
Wu Xin.

132
00:06:59,279 --> 00:07:00,079
Speak.

133
00:07:00,399 --> 00:07:01,199
Master,

134
00:07:01,439 --> 00:07:02,680
Lin Rulan was rescued by Liu Xin.

135
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,600
Magistrate Yu only caught Xiaotao.

136
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,680
Mr. Wang told me himself.

137
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:09,279
Her Highness ordered
him to find Lady Cheng'en in two days.

138
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,600
Otherwise...

139
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:11,920
Meng Wan.

140
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:16,600
Magistrate Yu has wanted
my "Spring River" painting for ages.

141
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,600
Fetch it and deliver it to him.

142
00:07:19,879 --> 00:07:20,920
Tell him

143
00:07:21,439 --> 00:07:22,600
that as long as he has Xiaotao,

144
00:07:23,199 --> 00:07:25,199
he can lure Lin Rulan out.

145
00:07:26,199 --> 00:07:27,519
Yes, Master.

146
00:07:28,079 --> 00:07:29,360
It's an official notice.

147
00:07:32,879 --> 00:07:34,680
No, I'm going to save her now.

148
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:35,399
Wait.

149
00:07:35,759 --> 00:07:36,560
It might be a trap.

150
00:07:37,759 --> 00:07:40,639
Ms. Huang, please go
check it out first.

151
00:07:41,759 --> 00:07:43,160
They're after you,

152
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,240
not Xiaotao.

153
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:45,759
Mr. Liu is right.

154
00:07:46,439 --> 00:07:47,680
Right now, all of us

155
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:50,000
are probably on the authorities' radar.

156
00:07:51,959 --> 00:07:52,759
Jiaojiao,

157
00:07:53,279 --> 00:07:54,959
you already took the money.

158
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:56,759
Do me one more favor.

159
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:58,800
Alright.

160
00:07:59,279 --> 00:08:00,439
You saved me back then.

161
00:08:00,639 --> 00:08:02,040
Call us even now.

162
00:08:07,639 --> 00:08:09,399
She seems tough and greedy,

163
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,480
but she has a good heart.

164
00:08:12,079 --> 00:08:12,680
Step back.

165
00:08:12,759 --> 00:08:13,319
Step back.

166
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,480
Back up, back up.

167
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:25,759
How awful.

168
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,199
Beat so badly.

169
00:08:32,279 --> 00:08:33,080
Jiaojiao,

170
00:08:33,279 --> 00:08:34,360
come see your sister.

171
00:08:35,159 --> 00:08:37,200
She has a red birthmark on her foot.

172
00:08:37,759 --> 00:08:40,879
It's a blessing for our family!

173
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,000
Sister.

174
00:08:50,039 --> 00:08:50,840
Sister.

175
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,120
So?

176
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,440
Did you find Xiaotao?

177
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:06,440
She's been hung from the city gate.

178
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,480
If she hangs much longer,

179
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:08,559
she'll die.

180
00:09:43,500 --> 00:09:46,460
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

181
00:09:46,700 --> 00:09:49,700
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

182
00:09:50,900 --> 00:09:53,660
♪The past no longer binds♪

183
00:09:54,140 --> 00:09:57,860
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

184
00:09:58,300 --> 00:10:02,420
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

185
00:10:03,260 --> 00:10:06,140
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

186
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:08,500
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

187
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:12,580
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

188
00:10:12,980 --> 00:10:15,180
♪For your faith that never broke♪

189
00:10:15,380 --> 00:10:19,500
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

190
00:10:20,380 --> 00:10:22,300
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

191
00:10:22,300 --> 00:10:26,540
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

192
00:10:27,740 --> 00:10:30,220
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

193
00:10:30,340 --> 00:10:32,980
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

194
00:10:32,980 --> 00:10:35,580
♪One thought turns into ash♪

195
00:10:36,540 --> 00:10:41,900
♪No future left to write♪

196
00:10:42,980 --> 00:10:44,780
♪If I never fall♪

197
00:10:44,820 --> 00:10:47,180
♪How could this waiting end♪

198
00:10:47,180 --> 00:10:48,540
♪If I bear no scars♪

199
00:10:48,540 --> 00:10:50,860
♪How could I challenge fate♪

200
00:10:50,860 --> 00:10:53,220
♪I knew there was no way back♪

201
00:10:53,220 --> 00:10:57,220
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

202
00:10:57,340 --> 00:10:59,460
♪For your faith that never broke♪

203
00:10:59,660 --> 00:11:03,620
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

204
00:11:04,580 --> 00:11:06,500
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

205
00:11:06,500 --> 00:11:10,900
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

206
00:11:11,980 --> 00:11:14,580
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

207
00:11:14,620 --> 00:11:17,180
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

208
00:11:17,180 --> 00:11:19,540
♪One thought turns into ash♪

209
00:11:20,660 --> 00:11:25,900
♪No future left to write♪

210
00:11:26,780 --> 00:11:29,180
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

211
00:11:30,460 --> 00:11:32,580
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

212
00:11:34,260 --> 00:11:36,460
♪If we meet again someday♪

213
00:11:36,900 --> 00:11:42,700
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪
